{"tid":2215460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬官拒設量刑委員會：不滿可上訴","createTime":"2020-09-24T04:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T05:38:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6abd7ec3ad0f643cdebb161dc986c4ed8ad77028","tid":2215460,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:19:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/LGIOFI2ECZFL5PKJIEH5ZUM3X4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FLGIOFI2ECZFL5PKJIEH5ZUM3X4%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=4fe7e146\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FLGIOFI2ECZFL5PKJIEH5ZUM3X4%2F&h=09c5ee17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/LGIOFI2ECZFL5PKJIEH5ZUM3X4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n馬官拒設量刑委員會：不滿可上訴<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近月建制派和左報唱雙簧，向政府施壓要求成立安插非法律界人士在內的量刑委員會，「指導」法庭以確保抗爭者獲「應有懲罰」。終審法院首席法官馬道立昨在聲明中反駁，強調量刑是司法職能，由法院獨立行使，而非政治問題，又稱若任何一方不滿判刑，可提出上訴或覆核，形容有關途徑是糾正被視為不足或過重刑罰的唯一恰當方法。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：罕有發14頁聲明  馬道立反擊左報「司法機構不容政治化」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9w_EcL4iqnGpFYq3oVcW9PZ6hH4=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V5HS6GT7KZAKZB5WRJCCWEQF2U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9w_EcL4iqnGpFYq3oVcW9PZ6hH4%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV5HS6GT7KZAKZB5WRJCCWEQF2U.jpg&h=4d61f8a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周浩鼎批評聲明未能令公眾對司法機構「行事公正」重拾信心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強調量刑為司法職能<br />\n<br />\n馬道立在聲明中指出，不時有輿論認為應設立量刑委員會，就所有刑事罪行發出具約束力的量刑標準，但他指出，量刑是一項司法職能，由法院獨立行使，亦是法院專有的職能。法庭每天要就大量不同案件量刑，每宗案件具體情況不同，要在每宗案件中判處公正而合適的刑罰，是法庭極具挑戰性及艱巨的工作，亦涉行使司法判斷以求取平衡的量刑決定。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立續指，法庭所判處的刑罰要取得公眾的尊重和信任，香港社會重視言論自由，。。。。。。。。。，「這是糾正一項被視為不足或過重的刑罰的唯一恰當方法」，而申請覆核責任在於代表檢控機關的律政司長。<br />\n<br />\n法律界立法會議員郭榮鏗認同馬道立對「量刑委員會」的回應，重申量刑必須由法院獨立行使，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，一直鼓吹成立「量刑委員會」的民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎及葛珮帆批評，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CohCzQDbHCGPC9NcGkJgEb0pXiY=/1843x1363/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZJ4C5LO2DVFQXA5IK2UR4IR4FY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCohCzQDbHCGPC9NcGkJgEb0pXiY%3D%2F1843x1363%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZJ4C5LO2DVFQXA5IK2UR4IR4FY.gif&h=f8cbbd7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95b2885cbdcb2c3b5cce0758a6326fade2ad6da1","tid":2215460,"uid":5943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"馬生瞓醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e234f05cb26fef47dd8a95dae3c56910a446faf","tid":2215460,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"同共產黨講法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7130f706f6e0c8eb11556acde744c52eb3e8e2c","tid":2215460,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:23:39.000Z","msg":"炒撚哂班賤種藍官，香港就真係有番法治"},{"pid":"fb7e50b0860bca6b27c0c8e8b250b7efedabd5b0","tid":2215460,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:24:57.000Z","msg":"算鳩數把啦, 無謂底褲當面褲著喇!"},{"pid":"843f86f29eb14d259e1f3e1f01d553d9e96d30ef","tid":2215460,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"法治早就冇撚左"},{"pid":"21fcadb70bc749fae4153e63f2f3e2073b5c1fc5","tid":2215460,"uid":202256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"屌 解散獨立重組就有用啦<br />\n法治撚有人想咩<br />\n守完法都換取唔到自己應有嘅權利<br />\n法治真真正正死亡果日<br />\n法治先有機會重生"},{"pid":"d01f4076ef3a31a5a020695d1002b4568595086f","tid":2215460,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dis